    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1887-08-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1887-08-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="485" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d485">
                <head>No. 485.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Manning</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-08-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 23,
                            1887</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 152.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: In connection with my instruction No. 147, of
                        12th instant, I have now the pleasure to inclose for your information, and
                        for such use as you may find it practicable, a copy of a telegram<note n="*" xml:id="d485fn1">Printed in Mr. Hall’s No. 697, <ref target="#pg_138">page 138</ref>, <hi rend="italic">supra.</hi>
                    </note> from your
                        colleague at Guatemala City, announcing that the Government of Salvador has
                        agreed to extend the same rebate to American vessels as conceded to<note n="*" xml:id="d485fn2">Printed in Mr. Hall’s No. 697, <ref target="#pg_138">page 138</ref>, <hi rend="italic">supra.</hi>
                    </note> Spanish Central American steamers.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">T. F. Bayard.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
